anything left to prove.

956
00:38:51.896 --> 00:38:53.898
(exhales)

957
00:38:58.703 --> 00:39:00.838
(Sheryl sobbing)

958
00:39:02.506 --> 00:39:06.410
Oh. no. God!

959
00:39:08.646 --> 00:39:11.882
No! No!

960
00:39:11.949 --> 00:39:14.752
(sirens wailing)

961
00:39:14.819 --> 00:39:16.420
It's okay.

962
00:39:17.188 --> 00:39:19.423
(indistinct chatter over radio)

963
00:39:23.427 --> 00:39:24.862
(siren chirps)

964
00:39:24.929 --> 00:39:26.163
(Bull sighs)

965
00:39:26.230 --> 00:39:28.799
STALLARD:
Hey. Bull. You okay?

966
00:39:28.866 --> 00:39:32.603
Hey. Yeah. I'm good. Thanks.

967
00:39:32.670 --> 00:39:35.439
Uh... Did you get
everything you need?

968
00:39:35.506 --> 00:39:36.707
I'm sure I'll have
more questions

969
00:39:36.774 --> 00:39:38.109
