for saving your life.

975
00:39:46.884 --> 00:39:48.986
I kind of remember
saving my own life.

976
00:39:49.053 --> 00:39:50.488
Please.

977
00:39:50.554 --> 00:39:53.090
My gun beats
your psychobabble any day.

978
00:39:53.157 --> 00:39:55.893
(scoffs)
Agree to disagree.

979
00:39:56.961 --> 00:39:57.895
Hey.

980
00:39:59.096 --> 00:40:00.965
Thank you.

